Referred specimens:
MPEF-PV
10557, carapacial remains; 
MPEF-PV
10558, carapacial remains; MPEF- PV 10559, carapacial remains; 
MPEF-PV
10560, 3rd cervical vertebra; 
MPEF-PV
10561, proximal end of right humerus; 
MPEF-PV
